  "detailed_description": "<h1>patch</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Game with a patch is sweet. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Press \"K\" and \"C\" on the login screen. You will reap sweet fruit.</p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1>\"Dream Rhythm\" is an addictive rhythm game.<br>Simple operation, beautiful songs, bring you a dreamy flow experience.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3115500/extras/3b01f94172ab3c5affd42eb6bb8512f0.poster.avif?t=1766152333\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3115500/extras/3b01f94172ab3c5affd42eb6bb8512f0.webm?t=1766152333\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3115500/extras/3b01f94172ab3c5affd42eb6bb8512f0.mp4?t=1766152333\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Game features</strong></h2>10 beautiful songs<br>Including Chinese, Japanese, Korean, Russian and English. Multiple styles, different experiences.<br><br>Simple operation<br>Only 2 buttons are needed to play the game. Anyone can get started quickly.<br><br>Each song contains 3 difficulties<br>Play the simple mode easily, practice in the normal mode, and finally challenge the hard mode!<br><br>Score leaderboard<br>Try to get a higher score and leave your name on the leaderboard!",
  "about_the_game": "\"Dream Rhythm\" is an addictive rhythm game.<br>Simple operation, beautiful songs, bring you a dreamy flow experience.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3115500/extras/3b01f94172ab3c5affd42eb6bb8512f0.poster.avif?t=1766152333\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3115500/extras/3b01f94172ab3c5affd42eb6bb8512f0.webm?t=1766152333\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3115500/extras/3b01f94172ab3c5affd42eb6bb8512f0.mp4?t=1766152333\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Game features</strong></h2>10 beautiful songs<br>Including Chinese, Japanese, Korean, Russian and English. Multiple styles, different experiences.<br><br>Simple operation<br>Only 2 buttons are needed to play the game. Anyone can get started quickly.<br><br>Each song contains 3 difficulties<br>Play the simple mode easily, practice in the normal mode, and finally challenge the hard mode!<br><br>Score leaderboard<br>Try to get a higher score and leave your name on the leaderboard!",
